				\begin{document}$$ V_{\text{oc}} = \left( {{\frac{kT}{\text{e}}}} \right){ \ln }\left( {{\frac{{J_{\text{inj}} }}{{n_{\text{cb}} k_{\text{et}} [{{\text{I}}_{3}}^{ - } ]}}}} \right), $$\end{document}where k and T are the Boltzmann constant and the cell temperature, respectively. e is the charge on the electron, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
				\usepackage{amssymb}
